{"tid":2287974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】aespa《Black Mamba》MV被韓網罵慘：這都什麼拍攝角度，麻煩給她們穿上褲子","createTime":"2020-11-16T07:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T08:21:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4827dda7399914d11de93a6a70f04a1da30f81","tid":2287974,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_a71387eaab6c33e814d916483dc76df8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131670-884965.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_a71387eaab6c33e814d916483dc76df8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131670-884965.png&h=6e147ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSM娛樂重磅打造的新女團aespa即將出道，關於成員的宣傳照、出道曲MV預告等也陸續公開，吸引了大批網友的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\naesap由WINTER、KARINA、寧寧和GISELLE4名女生組成，萬眾矚目的出道曲《Black Mamba》預告發佈之後，依舊是「爭議」不斷。 先是批評KARINA一個人佔盡了MV的2/3，被指是「皇族待遇」，對其他成員不公平。 接著，《Black Mamba》MV預告某些畫面疑似抄襲了K/DA，引得眾人吐槽SM娛樂是否是江郎才盡，都鬧出了「抄襲」這一套。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c82a3cceb4216c465e279cc1d80a06e8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131670-884966.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c82a3cceb4216c465e279cc1d80a06e8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131670-884966.png&h=0c9f81c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7567718e282200a7d70f265153969024/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-16/131670-884967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7567718e282200a7d70f265153969024%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-16%2F131670-884967.png&h=fd0ea4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而最讓人不解的就是MV的拍攝角度問題，這是一支平均年齡僅20.2歲的年輕女團，老幺寧寧甚至還是一名未成年者。而我們在MV裡看到了什麼？ 成員們穿著超短熱舞，其中一個舞蹈動作中，眾人蹲坐在地上扭轉上半身，角度正好對準了成員們的下半身，安全褲被一覽無餘。 後排的GISELLE所穿的安全褲和膚色幾乎無差別，猛一看真的會引發誤解，讓網友們看得很不舒服。（問題在13秒處）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mx0ZcpPQVBg&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dmx0ZcpPQVBg%26feature%3Demb_title&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3kzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=170df960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mx0ZcpPQVBg&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/eAeW5C1GTZWNo8diu3/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FeAeW5C1GTZWNo8diu3%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3234efaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nvia GIPHY<br />\n<br />\n有網友拿出了ITZY的MV作比對，兩隊有相似的趴地、劈腿的舞蹈動作。 ITZY的成員們所穿的短褲是正常的褲長，無論怎麼舞動，都不會走光。 某些鏡頭中，站在最前方的禮志甚至還穿著長褲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/OM1ni4Al2UJNxXwtTW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FOM1ni4Al2UJNxXwtTW%2Fgiphy.gif&h=351f53e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/aCWA3lYVY5aXhWoYBI/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FaCWA3lYVY5aXhWoYBI%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2a196aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣一對比，aespa的角度問題就更加明顯了，更是引爆了韓網的爭議，不少網友指責：「這都什麼年代了，還玩物化女性這一套」、「不能給孩子們穿上褲子嗎」、「aespa是 無辜的，她們只是被要求那樣穿」、「女團成員真可憐」、「這不是想像力，角度太明顯了，想裝作看不到都難」、「SM是瘋了吧，讓未成年穿成這樣跳舞」等。<br />\n<br />\naespa算是一支自帶話題的女團。 近1個月的出道宣傳期伴隨著各類爭議，真心不希望一隻打造了多年的女團走「營銷團」路線。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：theqoo、ITZY、vespa」"},{"pid":"43d97625d5f4563696cc81c11729e61b621c1671","tid":2287974,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">愈反愈紅</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0763a29c7228721c5913c0d9ec300a50d072b4b","tid":2287974,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:11:23.